high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door you can see behind the table then turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the keys you see on the table.
Turn around and walk until you're about two feet from the green garbage and turn left and walk to the red couch and turn right to walk to the red wall then turn left and walk to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp as you hold keys.

high_descs: Turn around and walk halfway across the room, then turn right and walk across the room before turning right to walk to the table.
Take the keys that are next to the newspaper off the table.
Turn to the right and walk across the room to the trash bin, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: To look at the keys in the light.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the dining table.
Pick up the key chain on the table that is to the left of the newspaper.
Turn around and walk to the front of the floor lamp in the top right corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Examine a key chain by the light of a floor lamp.
